UVAT TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 43.30% to NT$32,375,000 from NT$57,100,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales             32,375           57,100    
YOY%             -43.30%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            171,281          313,655    
YOY%             -45.39% 
=================================================================
 